{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"b97e0fe368","title":"在河南省文联文学座谈会上的发言","origin":"《苏金伞右派集团言论与作品》（河南省文学美术工作者联合会，1958年）。 ","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"1dde392179","index":0,"year":1957,"month":6,"day":1,"articleId":"b97e0fe368"}],"tags":[{"id":"7aac50a8c5","name":"文艺战线","type":"主题/事件"},{"id":"e23dcf99fa","name":"发言","type":"文稿类型"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"CCRD-fanyou","name":"中国反右运动数据库","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":""}],"authors":[{"id":"9ec5840208","name":"河南"},{"id":"e8dd4600fb","name":"张乡朴"}]},"publication_details":{"CCRD-fanyou":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"7438b82cbd","type":"title","text":"在河南省文联文学座谈会上的发言","index":0,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"b97e0fe368"},{"id":"7a6bd95b2a","type":"authors","text":"河南张乡朴","index":1,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"b97e0fe368"},{"id":"d31e7a7561","type":"subtitle","text":"(张乡朴：戏剧家)","index":2,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"b97e0fe368"},{"id":"5f72c20d8c","type":"paragraph","text":"我省小说、诗歌创作力量雄厚，剧本作者少，没发表园地。以前《河南日报》副刊还发表。现在也学《人民日报》第八版，也不要剧本了。《河南文艺》改版后也不发表了，同时有排挤剧本的现象。本来剧本的作者弱，又无发表园地，剧作者已到穷途末路。","index":3,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"b97e0fe368"},{"id":"dfd95c557d","type":"paragraph","text":"关于剧本评奖，有些作品还达不到发表水平也评奖，这是笑话。我的意见，评奖是个好办法，可以在一两年内评一次，要大家公认的好作品。","index":4,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"b97e0fe368"},{"id":"fb9882e0fc","type":"paragraph","text":"文化局变成了武化局。","index":5,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"b97e0fe368"},{"id":"3c6cb7c975","type":"paragraph","text":"文化局在批评演员表演中的形式主义；旧演员就是形式主义。形成一批人整一批人。","index":6,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"b97e0fe368"},{"id":"df1aceabdc","type":"paragraph","text":"编辑部对来稿要少改、不要把内容都改了。我给《郑州日报》写的稿子，十句话没有我的两句话，题目改成和李准的一样了。当天我真想把稿费退回去。","index":7,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"b97e0fe368"},{"id":"c3b61bc34d","type":"paragraph","text":"党的领导和文化局领导要经常看文艺作品，不然给作者联系就没有共同语言。","index":8,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"b97e0fe368"}],"page":{"id":"4e1be26848","publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"b97e0fe368","start":0,"end":0}}}},"__N_SSG":true}